				<h1>How is Bloom different?</h1>
			</div>


			<p>Instead of paying a monthly rate with no guarantee, our payment structure is geared towards only being charged for the traffic you receive.{{!--  This is monitored through favInstead of paying a monthly subscription with no guarantee, our payment structure is geared towards only being charged for the traffic and bookings you receive. --}} This is monitored through favouriting, contact requests and direct messaging. With a capped monthly spend you can manage your budget.{{!-- ouriting, contact number requests and direct messaging. --}}</p>
