				<p style="text-align: left;">
				It is our priority to drive value to the vendor and the user.
				<br><br>No subscription fees and you can leave the platform at any time.
				<br><br>Inquiries are sent directly to your inbox.
				<br><br>Without enquiries, contact requests or favouriting, no costs will be added to you.
				<br><br>You will never pay more than your capped monthly spend and still receive the traffic as usual.
				<br><br>We aim to offer a fully transparent service that shows you the traffic you receive with itemized billing.
				<br><br>Along with your bill, you will receive a monthly analytics report.
				<br><br>This valuable information provides insights into your profile, such as how to increase traffic to your listing along with so much more.			
				<br><br>Our targeted marketing strategy helps you gain exposure to couples that are in the market for wedding vendors. As a digital business we put a huge focus on online marketing in order to drive maximum user traffic to our platform and ultimately your products and services.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="form-group" style="padding-top: 50px; padding-bottom: 80px;">
				{{#link-to 'vendor-signup'}}{{mdl-button isRaised=true text='Sign Up'}}{{/link-to}}
			</div><hr>
		</div>
